{"header":{"word":"חָעַק","entry":8261,"letter":"ח","strongs":6817,"page":858},"definitions":[{"title":"Def","body":" &#134; [[חָעַק]] ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"vb.","body":" cry, cry out, call (&#8214;[[זׇעַק]]; NH id.; Ar. s.a9aqa perhaps orig. sound as thunder, cf. s.a09iqah;un thunderbolt, s.a9iqa bellow (of bull));&#8212;","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"Qal","body":" Pf. 3 ms.&#180;[[ח]] 1Ki 20:39, La 2:18, 3 fs. [[חָֽעֲקָה]] De 22:24 +, etc.; Impf. [[יִחְעַק]] Ex 23:22 +, etc.; Imv. fs. [[וְחַעֲקִי]] Je 22:20, [[וּחֳעָָקִי]] v:Je 22:20; fpl. [[חְעַקְנׇה]] Je 49:3; Inf. abs. [[חָעׂק]] Ex 22:22; cstr. [[לִחְעׂק]] 2Ki 8:3; Pt. fs. abs. [[חׂעֶ֫קֶת]] 2Ki 8:5; mpl. [[חׂעֲקִים]] Ge 4:10, Ex 5:8; &#8212;","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"1.","body":" cry, cry out, for help, usu. c. [[אֶל]] pers.;&#8212;","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"a.","body":" unto man Ge 41:55 (E; + [[ל]] rei), Nu 11:3 (JE), 1Ki 20:39, 2Ki 6:26, 2Ki 8:3 (+ [[אֶל]] rei), v:2Ki 8:5 (+ [[עַל]] rei); sq. [[אמר]] Ex 5:15 (J), 2Ki 4:1 and ([[אֶל]] pers. om.) Ex 5:8 (J), 2Ki 4:40, 2Ki 6:5. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"b.","body":" esp. unto &#180;[[י]]: Ge 4:10, Ex 8:8 ( + [[עַל־]] [[דְּבַר]] rei), Ex 14:10, Ex 14:15, Ex 15:25, Ex 17:4, Ex 22:22 ([[חָעׂק יִחְעַק]]), v:Ex 22:26, Nu 12:13, Nu 20:16, Jos 24:7 (all JE), Ju Jdg 4:3, Jdg 10:12, De 26:7, Is 19:20 (+ [[מִפְּנֵי]] rei), La 2:18, Ne 9:27, Ps 107:6, Ps 107:28; [[קוֹלִי]] [[וְאֶחְעָָקָה]] &#180;[[אֶל־א]] Ps 77:2, cf. Ps 34:18; c.&#180;[[לי]] 2Ch 13:14: [[נֶגְדֱֶָּ]] Ps 88:2. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"c.","body":" cry unto ([[אֶל]]) idol Is 46:7. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"2.","body":" abs. cry, cry out, in distress, need;&#8212;Ge 27:34 (J; c. acc. cogn.), De 22:24, De 22:27, 1Sa 33:7 (&#8214;[[בָּכָה]]), Is 65:14 (&#8214;[[הֵילִיל]], opp. [[רָנַן]]; c. [[מִן]] rei), Je 22:20, Je 22:20 (&#8214;[[נָתַן קוֹל]]), Je 49:3 (&#8214;[[הֵילִיל]]), Job 35:12; c. obj. [[חָמָס]] Job 19:7 (&#8214;[[אֲשַׁוַּע]]). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"3.","body":" make outcry, clamour, Is 42:2 (+ [[יִשָּׂא]], [[יַשְׁמִיעַ]] [[קוֹלוֹ]] ). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"Niph.","body":" be summoned (i.e. to arms), abs.; Impf. 3 ms. [[וַיִּצָּעֵק]] Ju Jdg 7:23, Jdg 7:24, Jdg 12:1, so 3 mpl. [[וַיִּצָּֽעֲקוּ]] Jdg 10:17, 2Ki 3:21, sq. [[אַחֲרֵי שָׁאוּל]] + acc. loc. 1Sa 13:4. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"Pi.","body":" Pt. [[מְחַעֵק]] cry aloud, in grief, 2Ki 2:12. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"Hiph.","body":" call together [[הַמִּחְפָּה]] &#180;[[וַיַּחְעֵקאֶת־הָעָם אֶל־י]] 1Sa 10:17.\r","content":"definition","show":"block"}],"notes":"","etymology":[],"morphology":[]}